01:21:40,784 --> 01:21:41,956
Por supuesto.

1563
01:21:42,069 --> 01:21:43,749
John. John Celestine.

1564
01:21:43,862 --> 01:21:45,302
Por supuesto, John.

1565
01:21:45,709 --> 01:21:49,146
Soy Howard Cummings,
Kaminsky es mi apellido de soltero.

1566
01:21:50,202 --> 01:21:53,338
